  "description": "The siphonophore colony at rest. Pluck brightness low (0.25) — no sharp attack, just a soft bloom of string. Grain size large (0.72) for long, smooth microsound clouds. Swarm depth minimal (0.12) keeps the colony still and unified. Gentle resonance (0.28). Long attack (0.4s) and release (2.2s). The goddess harp lulls something ancient to sleep.",
